nodes.text: Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back Manga
Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back Manga is a manga version of Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back. It is written by Toshiki Kudo and was released on September 21, 2018.

Relive the incredible story of the original sequel to George Lucas' Star Wars in this uniquely adapted manga collection. Follow Luke Skywalker as he heads to the planet Dagobah to train with Jedi master Yoda. Meanwhile, Han Solo, Princess Leia and the rest of the rebels struggle to outrun the Empire's fleet, finding themselves heading straight into a trap set by evil Darth Vader.
